SolAR, Solution for Augmented Reality

you will find information about SolAR in the following sections

  • Discover will give you general information about the SolAR Framework project

  • Use it explains how to use SolAR framework quickly, and more in depth for experts or future contributors

  • Contribute will give information for all SolAR contributors, as SolAR is open-source

  • API will be helpful for all SolAR developers : contributors and users.

By using SolAR, you can easily build augmented reality applications by testing different vision based localization solutions, create and share your own camera pose estimation pipeline with the community, and even develop efficient low-level processing elements to meet specific requirements.

SolAR is a framework that improves interoperability for augmented reality applications and offers efficiency and robustness thanks to a modular software pipeline architecture.
